UNLIMEAT Jerky has high  amount of protein, as high as beef jerky, but is 100% plant-based. Not only can you avoid the many health risks that come from eating processed meat, you also reduce your carbon footprint by eating less meat. We added authentic Korean BBQ and spicy seasonings that made the jerky super flavorful.

We also gave our jerky an incredible beefy texture. 

We even removed all the cholesterol, removed fat, and we made UNLIMEAT with no artificial ingredients or preservatives.

Tone: attractive

Audience: Parents
